OL,7,FTV Presenter Edith Bowman has made a
OL,8,Fdirect appeal to thieves who took her
OL,9,Fbag which contained her grandfather's
OL,10,Fashes.
OL,12,FThe incident happened on Friday on a
OL,13,Ftrain travelling from London
OL,14,FPaddington to Cheltenham.
OL,16,FShe shared the plea on her Instagram
OL,17,Fstories and warned people to keep an
OL,18,Feye out for her bad, which she
OL,19,Fdescribed as a dark green, old school
OL,20,Fcase with brown straps around it.
