OL,7,FThe former BBC Radio 1 presenter said:
OL,8,F"Not the day I was really hoping for,
OL,9,Fto be honest.
OL,11,F"I just got on the train at London
OL,12,FPaddington, the 9:32 to Cheltenham,
OL,13,Fgot Kemble, and some **** has stolen
OL,14,Fmy case.
OL,16,F"If you are that person who took,
OL,17,Fsomeone else's luggage off the train
OL,18,Fbetween London and Kemble, please can
OL,19,Fyou return it to the nearest station,
OL,20,Fand I'd very much appreciate that."
